        <a href='/venezuelas-environmental-collapse-a-harbinger-of-health-and-environmental-harm/' class='c-teaser'>
          <div class='c-teaser__content'>
            <h3 class='c-teaser__title'>Venezuela&#x27;s Environmental Collapse: A Harbinger of Health and Environmental Harm</h3>
            <time class='c-teaser__date' datetime='2021-08-18' title='18 August 2021'>18.Aug.2021</time>
          </div>
